⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Ivan Karamazov
node BKZ · BKZ · ⟦Ivan Karamazov:BKZ:daf2db⟧

WHO   — Ivan Karamazov — the intellect · the rebel
WHAT  — The intellect that builds the case against God (the Rebellion, the Grand Inquisitor) and whose ‘all is permitted’ Smerdyakov turns into murder.
WHERE — BKZ · The Brothers Karamazov  Framework inputs: The Brothers Karamazov (Dostoevsky, 1880)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the novel needs its unbelief stated by a genius — and then needs that genius to discover his own complicity and break.
HOW   — By argument, pride, and a detachment that shatters when the devil (his own shabby double) comes to mock him into brain fever.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I returned the ticket to a heaven bought with a child's tears — and learned, too late, that my clean idea had hands, and they killed my father.

